Text:
Works great on my Galaxy S using Andriod 2.1.
NB. After following the downloading the data from Gameloft, go back to Airplane mode before you continue as the game restarts and will try to log on to their servers to register the game, hence the fake program notice.
@wallerius2003, simply uninstall and reinstall in airplane mode and follow my tips to enjoy the game. Always launch the game with 3g and wifi off.
